Character Mixamo to Unity https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IeujTg71QoE
- if you have no textures in unity after downloading characterhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xOeodlLTx8g


- download character and animation (bei running animation: IN PLACE anklicken)
- drag and drop in unity
- Asset Aj -> extract textures -> save textures in materials 
- AJ needs an animator in inspector, From the Rig tab of the Inspector window, set the Animation Type to Humanoid. 
      By default, the Avatar Definition property is set to Create From This Model. 
      If you keep this option, Unity attempts to map the set of bones defined in the file to a Humanoid Avatar.
- create controler for AJ
- drag and drop controler on AJ/animator in inspector
- double click on controler -> create idle state in transition to entry
- connect idle animation with idle state
- idle state soll immer wieder ausgeführt werden -> Idle -> Edit -> Loop Time active -> Apply
- wenn man neue ANimation hinzufügen will, muss diese mit Idle verknüpft sein im Animator 
